ize:14px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">Use of the parasightdemo.com/vivara/ website is available and permitted&nbsp;to persons only who are competent and can form a legally binding contract under the Indian Contract Act, of 1872. We do not knowingly receive/ collect any data or information from children who are under the age of 18 years and not eligible to form a legally binding contract under the Indian Contract Act, of 1872. But if you have shared any data or information of children (who are under the age of 18 years) with us, you explicitly represent that you have the absolute authority to do so and you permit us to use such shared data or information in accordance with our this Privacy Policy.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#444444\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\">2. COLLECTION OF YOUR INFORMATION</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">From time to time, whenever you use the parasightdemo.com/vivara/ website and its services or otherwise interact with us, we collect and store your data or personal information relating to your identity and demographic information. In addition to this, if you use&nbsp;this website by using your maintained Google or Facebook account and their login credentials, even in this situation, we collect and store your data or personal information and other information associated with those third-party sites/ social networking&nbsp;sites i.e. Google or Facebook. Please note that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">when you use this website through social networking sites i.e. Google or Facebook, you expressly authorize us to collect, store, use, process or share your data, personal information and other information associated with those third-party sites/&nbsp;social networking&nbsp;sites in accordance with our this Privacy policy. Kindly note that w</span><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">e may also collect your data or personal information from our associated affiliates, associates, third-party&nbsp;service providers, banking&nbsp;partner, payment partners, shipping partners&nbsp;or commercially available sources. Further, certain&nbsp;information about you may be automatically tracked by us as per your browsing/ shopping behaviour on our this website. Our primary goal to do so is to provide you with the best possible, easy, safe, smooth, hassle-free and a very enjoyable world-class online shopping experience on this website because we consider it very necessary in order to enhance&nbsp;your online shopping experience day by day much better, safer and easier on our this website. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">We may keep records of communication between you and us for the purposes of our services administration, user administration, training, business management, research and business development and business intelligence. We may share/ disclose such records of communication with third parties when it is required by law or when it is&nbsp;required&nbsp;to provide/facilitate our&nbsp;users&nbsp;with our&nbsp;services.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">If you want to just browse our this&nbsp;website and/ or products then you are not required to provide any of your information to us. But if you want to use our website, this is mandatory for you&nbsp;to create your membership account on this website. Once you created your membership account on this website by providing your data or personal information to us then&nbsp;you become no longer anonymous to us.&nbsp;Normally wherever possible on this website, we indicate required and optional fields and you always have the option to provide or not to provide information by selecting to use or not to use&nbsp;any particular service or feature on this website. Kindly note that you&nbsp;voluntarily provide your data or personal&nbsp;information to us. You have the right&nbsp;to remove/ withdraw your consent. At any time,&nbsp;If you wish to remove/ withdraw your consent, you have the option to remove/ withdraw your consent by writing to our&nbsp;Grievance Officer at the contact details&nbsp;given below. Please don&#39;t forget to mention &quot;Withdrawal of my consent for processing my data or personal information&quot; in the main subject line of your communication. After completion of the verification process of your consent withdrawal request, we will act on it. Please&nbsp;note that the withdrawal of your consent will not be retrospective. This&nbsp;will be in accordance with our this Privacy Policy and Terms &amp; Conditions of this website under the applicable laws. In the event, which&nbsp;you withdraw your consent&nbsp;from us under this Privacy Policy, we reserve the right to restrict or disallow&nbsp;the provision of our services for which we consider&nbsp;such data or personal information very necessary.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">Further, we consider it our duty to inform you that generally, we use the services of our&nbsp;associated&nbsp;third-party payment gateway provider in order to receive payments <span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">from you on this website</span>. Though we take utmost care and precautions in order to work with our&nbsp;third-party payment gateway provider we do&nbsp;not have any control over our&nbsp;payment gateway provider&#39;s&nbsp;systems, servers, technology and workflows. Further, we&nbsp;do not&nbsp;collect your Transactional Data/ Payment Information and Details i.e. Bank Account or Credit Card or Debit Card or Net-Banking or Mobile Banking or E-Wallet or Other Payment Instrument Details&nbsp;because when you make a purchase on our website by using your Payment Card&nbsp;or Other Payment Instrument, you are automatically redirected from this website to directly our associated, reputed, fast, secure and well trust