g or incomplete bank details to us&nbsp;in this regard, we will not be held responsible and/ or liable for any loss or damage to you.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#5e5e5e\">You expressly represent, undertake and confirm that all the data or personal information which you provide to us from time to time shall&nbsp;be true, correct, accurate, authentic, current, valid and complete in all manner and you have all the reasonable rights, permissions, licenses and consents to provide such data or personal information to us. You also represent, undertake and confirm that&nbsp;your providing data or personal information and Vivara&#39;s resultant&nbsp;storage, collection, usage, transfer, access or processing of the same data or personal information shall not be in violation of any third party agreement, laws, rules and regulations, judgements, orders or decrees.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">SAFETY INSTRUCTION:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#212529\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">If you receive a telephone/ mobile call or an email or a mobile sms or a WhatsApp chat message or a text message from any other source&nbsp;from a person/ company/ agency/ association claiming to be from Vivara seeking your sensitive personal data or&nbsp;information like Credit/ Debit Card Expiry, PIN, and CVV Numbers or Net-Banking or Mobile banking or E-Wallets OTP (One Time Password),&nbsp;Password, we request you to never provide such data or information to that person/ company/ agency/ association. We at Vivara or our associated affiliates, associates, third-party service providers, banking partner, payment&nbsp;partners, shipping partners and staff do not at any time connect with you requesting such data or information. If you have already revealed such data or information, please report it immediately to an Appropriate Law Enforcement Agency accord